trans-unit.source: NOTEBots are not allowed! The use of bots in the game is prohibited. It should not be the purpose of the game to automate processes. Such behaviour would make the game experience neither interesting nor exciting. Please abide by this rule and join us in creating a fair game for all.
If you do not have an account yet, click here.
The username must have between 2 and 32 characters.
Your password has to be at least 8 characters long, it must contain at least one uppercase letter, one lowercase letter and one number.
